---

This project includes code copied from and derived from the following:

OpenTelemetry Go Instrumentation
  - Source: https://github.com/open-telemetry/opentelemetry-go-instrumentation
  - License: Apache-2.0
  - Copyright: The OpenTelemetry Authors

  The following components were copied and adapted for the GoAkt eBPF agent:
  - internal/include (eBPF C headers)
  - internal/process
  - internal/structfield
  - internal/inject
  - internal/instrumentation (config, manager, probe, bpffs, kernel, context, pdataconv, debug)
  - pipeline and pipeline/otelsdk

  The GoAkt-specific instrumentation probes (internal/instrumentation/bpf/github.com/tochemey/goakt/actor/)
  use patterns and structure from OpenTelemetry Go Instrumentation but are original implementations.
